      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHE'S ALL FIRE (2) had won two in a row before finishing second (25.48) last time at this track. Solid record here winning two races. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from three starts. Can measure up this time. SECRET STORY (1) is a progressive type who recorded his 20th career win last time out (25.50) at this track. Has a strong winning record here at this journey. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Should be in this for a long way. EXTRA VOLTAGE (7) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 25.38 beating SHE'S ALL FIRE. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. One of main contenders. ARMARTA (3) showed good early speed and won last start. Sure to run well again.",
